# Wearable Motion Classifier

Real-time wearable human activity recognition system using ESP32-S3 and IMU sensing.

## Hardware
- ESP32-S3
- IMU sensor
- OLED display

## Pipeline
IMU → Filtering → Windowing → Feature Extraction → Classification

## Current Status
- [x] PlatformIO setup
- [x] ESP32 firmware upload
- [ ] IMU integration
- [ ] Signal processing
- [ ] Motion classification